sentences: Han Seung-woo (Korean: 한승우, born December 24, 1994), also known mononymously as Seungwoo, is a South Korean singer-songwriter, rapper, dancer and actor.
He debuted as a member of South Korean group Victon in 2016.
In 2019, he finished third on Produce X 101 and became a member of X1.
He debuted as a solo artist in August 2020 with the extended play Fame.
Han was born on December 24, 1994 in Busan, South Korea.
